embedcharge dry-run
&cntrl
 imin=0, irest=1, ntx=5, cut=12.0, dt=0.0005,
 ntb=0, ntt=0, ntpr=1, ntwx=1, ntwr=2, nstlim=2, ifqnt=1,
/
